{"tid":1880144,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得睇戲食爆谷嘅人好低賤","createTime":"2020-02-14T15:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T04:22:42.000Z","uid":44285,"like":66,"dislike":296,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0cb29c5dc806df5cc770da17ab40fdca5dec6f","tid":1880144,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"話說今日約咗女朋友睇小丑女 隔離個毒撚喺到食爆谷食到摺摺聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就心諗：吖屌你老母睇戲就睇戲食乜嘢爆谷？<br />\n<br />\n最後頂唔撚順佢一手倒咗佢啲爆谷落地 <br />\n條友仲要眼濕濕緊執返啲喺地下啲爆谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba4098f08940938668da21a0996101fd91aaadb","tid":1880144,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e543db342cb923c2d8bf324cb12999915eb397","tid":1880144,"uid":29080,"like":17,"dislike":6,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:29:45.000Z","msg":"我食著片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2172867d5cb2dc6d09526243c46b8dc76d373fa4","tid":1880144,"uid":224533,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:30:37.000Z","msg":"死tb恰毒撚"},{"pid":"bbbb3a6c6494a69557f1b1695f0d01c2a96c20bc","tid":1880144,"uid":127454,"like":128,"dislike":4,"score":124,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:30:38.000Z","msg":"屌人唔駛付出代價？<br />\n唔敢出聲叫on9仔<br />\n凈係回擊你已經算好<br />\n我認我係咸濕<br />\n有咩問題 你都一樣姐<br />\n我入唔入嚟又關你咩事啊<br />\n攬炒契弟<br />\n唔好以為自己大過我就好撚巴閉<br />\n你都係頭入嚟個批人<br />\n我無話想得罪邊個<br />\n不過你條仆街進嚟撩尻我 都幾好嘢<br />\n幾大啊你 2字頭3字頭定話4字頭？<br />\n都唔細啦 咁唔成熟<br />\n唔好以為上嚟發洩我就唔敢還擊<br />\n你老母上嚟callin都唔夠膽啦<br />\n我中唔中四又關你撚事？<br />\n中四唔撚俾咸濕？<br />\n駛唔駛戒埋淫慾啊<br />\n你自己呢個年紀同我咪差唔多<br />\n雙重標準<br />\n話我入嚟成人台係弱智<br />\n咁你咪仲撚弱智<br />\n你自己都睇緊啦<br />\n講撚咗幾多次<br />\n你有你道理你拎出嚟講<br />\n無事撩尻我 咁樣叫柒<br />\n我做咩柒事 柒得過你咁撚幼稚咩<br />\n我而家屌撚醒你班連登仔<br />\n咪撚咁幼稚 你IG又擺咩icon啊<br />\n有幾成熟？<br />\n係成熟你都唔會理我啦 你老母<br />\n我未撚出社會個邏輯都正路過你啦<br />\n攬炒契弟"},{"pid":"3b6ca4a988caede6161c5b256f209fbd36ca3cad","tid":1880144,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"6ba4098f08940938668da21a0996101fd91aaadb","tid":1880144,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"食其他嘢唔好？係都要煩到人咁撚自私"},{"pid":"259fb865cdd0977fd45f5db98dafd87962fd37d5","tid":1880144,"uid":179782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb0cb29c5dc806df5cc770da17ab40fdca5dec6f","tid":1880144,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"話說今日約咗女朋友睇小丑女 隔離個毒撚喺到食爆谷食到摺摺聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就心諗：吖屌你老母睇戲就睇戲食乜嘢爆谷？<br />\n<br />\n最後頂唔撚順佢一手倒咗佢啲爆谷落地 <br />\n條友仲要眼濕濕緊執返啲喺地下啲爆谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:31:05.000Z","msg":"仲有一路睇戲一路傾計果d"},{"pid":"fb8536dd44abace3d78f7c9832e4e75058cd7c85","tid":1880144,"uid":70195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"今晚有冇同條女去鋸扒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2245f78c6ce7a8a38f5018cc3dea61f46c168f6b","tid":1880144,"uid":273999,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fb0cb29c5dc806df5cc770da17ab40fdca5dec6f","tid":1880144,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"話說今日約咗女朋友睇小丑女 隔離個毒撚喺到食爆谷食到摺摺聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就心諗：吖屌你老母睇戲就睇戲食乜嘢爆谷？<br />\n<br />\n最後頂唔撚順佢一手倒咗佢啲爆谷落地 <br />\n條友仲要眼濕濕緊執返啲喺地下啲爆谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=