mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"你就係個死毒撚？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:39:49.000Z","msg":"失禮 你就係果條柒頭皮？"},{"pid":"8e71af5976cdacc5610f32939d0da0b4b809b184","tid":1880144,"uid":23170,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"屌，原來就係你條死仆街。我今日同仔仔睇戲，睇到戲肉聽到勁大聲之後就有個人喊緊。一望去後面見到條死柒頭拖住件肥芝企喺到恰個細路。成地都係爆谷。<br />\n<br />\n個職員入到嚟帶住兩個保安拖住你哋出去，你條女又叫又嗌，個保安拖佢出去嗰時又係咁將保安隻手放落自己對波，喺度大嗌非禮。成套戲最緊張嗰十分鐘就俾你哋兩條友破撚壞晒。好彩最後我同條仔互射兩次條氣先順返啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好地地睇戲搞乜撚人啲爆谷呀，咁叻包場呀笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e799c3e357a05af2d032228a3037dc22bc1dc9d","tid":1880144,"uid":150649,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:40:44.000Z","msg":"戲院可以比狗入?"},{"pid":"bc38ecebb31d0a1f12598ad1987690b6f08ab790","tid":1880144,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65f62f4dc6b518cbf2629bc62dd8b2545fc601f8","tid":1880144,"uid":266755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"02e90bbff86448799dc8853186ea2fe6702a3155","tid":1880144,"uid":266755,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"以前食魷魚，食煙，食蔗，食鹽焗花生，食鷄肶，食鹽焗蛋，食紅鷄腳，滷水鴨腳鴨腎，碗仔翅。直程成個buffet搬入去食都得添。<br />\n而家淨喺食爆谷濕濕碎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"午夜場如果套戲仔仔地，啲鷄骨呀，蔗頭蔗尾就會脫頴而出。好似啲愛國者導彈咁飛上銀幕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb64f3548f35d5dbc2e8e6c6e842484c3d288d57","tid":1880144,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e799c3e357a05af2d032228a3037dc22bc1dc9d","tid":1880144,"uid":150649,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:40:44.